                            <p>If you are considering hiring Garry, you will be pleased to have a strong, technically astute 
                                Developer within your organization.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center testimonial">
                            <img class="rounded-circle me-3" src="images/user3.png" alt="User 3">
